&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re excited about working in a fast-paced, high-growth environment and want to take the next step in your Finance career, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a driven and analytical &lt;strong&gt;(Junior) Finance Manager (FP&amp;amp;A)&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Finance team in Berlin. In this role, you’ll take ownership of core financial planning and analysis activities, including monthly management reporting, forecasting, budgeting, and financial modeling. You’ll work closely with senior finance leadership and cross-functional stakeholders to translate data into insights that shape strategic decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
