&lt;li&gt;Drive &lt;strong&gt;forecasting, budgeting, and long-term financial planning&lt;/strong&gt;, improving accuracy and transparency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain &lt;strong&gt;financial models&lt;/strong&gt; to support strategic, investment, and operational decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automate and scale FP&amp;amp;A processes&lt;/strong&gt;, including improving data structures, dashboards, and ad-hoc analyses to enable accurate, data-driven decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with business stakeholders to &lt;strong&gt;translate operational data into actionable financial insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
