&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Hive, we&#39;re building the most customer-centric operations platform in Europe — and our Merchant Care team is at the heart of that mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Merchant Care Associate — On the Ground&lt;/strong&gt;, you&#39;ll be the first point of contact for our merchants&#39; operational issues &lt;strong&gt;directly from the fulfillment center&lt;/strong&gt;. You&#39;ll work shoulder-to-shoulder with our logistics partner&#39;s floor teams, spot issues before they escalate, and close the loop between what&#39;s happening on the warehouse floor and our merchants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be &lt;strong&gt;on-site in Poznan&lt;/strong&gt;, part of Hive&#39;s Merchant Care team, and the bridge between the fulfillment center operations, Hive&#39;s office-based specialists, and our merchants.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be&lt;/strong&gt; the go-to Merchant Care contact at the fulfillment center: resolve issues that need a pair of eyes on the floor (missing items, inventory discrepancies, packaging questions, returns edge-cases).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own&lt;/strong&gt; the support tickets (Zendesk) routed directly to the fulfillment center queue — investigate, action, and resolve.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner&lt;/strong&gt; daily with the logistics partner Team and our Spec Ops — join their stand-ups, build trust, unblock.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spot&lt;/strong&gt; inefficiencies and proactively improve Merchant Care processes as we scale the on-site model.&lt;/li&gt;
