&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BER3 is our Berlin flagship - and the site where we pilot the processes, tools, and automation that later scale across the whole Hive network. We&#39;re looking for a Site Lead to own it end-to-end: its people, its performance, its P&amp;amp;L, and its standard of excellence. You&#39;ll run a site of ~200 associates across all different areas leading through a team of Area Managers. This is a hands-on leadership role - you set the standard on the floor, not from a desk. You&#39;re first in and last out when it matters, calm under pressure, and you turn problems into proposals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
