&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;and collaborate&lt;/strong&gt;. Write clearly (SOPs, incident post-mortems), present with structure (leadership reviews, all-hands), and own escalations end-to-end: including a fast, structured response on critical (SEV1) incidents. Partner with HQ, the WMS/product team, and merchant-facing teams.&lt;/li&gt;
